data.description: SELLER WILL CONTRIBUTE 5K TOWARDS BUYERS CLOSING COSTS OR RATE BUYDOWN! SOUTH of I-10, located in Antioch school district, and within 30 minutes of all area bases! Excellent opportunity to own this 2011 built home with 4 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms, located on an almost 1/3 acre lot. Roomy open floor plan features vaulted ceilings, hardwood floors, and a semi-open kitchen to living room layout. Granite countertops can be found in the kitchen and refrigerator, dishwasher, and microwave are less than 1 year old. Large master suite features master bathroom with double vanities, spacious walk-in closet, soaking tub as well as separate shower. Split floor plan allows for the additional 3 bedrooms to be located on the other side of the home. HUGE backyard is fully fenced! Additional exterior features include large driveway with ample parking opportunities, whole house gutters, and sprinkler system. Septic tank was recently pumped - May 2023. Add this one to your list and schedule your showing today!
